OL,3,CThree dead after San Diego mosque
OL,4,Cshooting as two teenage suspects found
OL,5,Cdead
OL,7,FThree people have been killed in a
OL,8,Fshooting at a mosque in San Diego, as
OL,9,Ftwo suspects were found dead, US
OL,10,Fpolice have said.
OL,12,FBoth suspects are believed to be
OL,13,Fteenagers, and the case is considered
OL,14,Fto be a hate crime, San Diego Police
OL,15,FChief Scott Wahl said at a press
OL,16,Fconference.
OL,18,FWahl said police were called to a car
OL,19,Freported to be stopped in the middle
OL,20,Fof a street near the site of the
OL,21,Fmosque.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
