OL,3,CThree dead after San Diego mosque
OL,4,Cshooting as two teenage suspects found
OL,5,Cdead
OL,7,FHe said two people "who we believe to
OL,8,Fbe the shooters in this incident, both
OL,9,Fdeceased" appeared to have self-
OL,10,Finflicted gunshot wounds.
OL,12,FThe shooting happened at the Islamic
OL,13,FCenter of San Diego, the largest
OL,14,Fmosque in San Diego County.
OL,16,FThe Islamic centre is about nine miles
OL,17,Fnorth of downtown San Diego.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
