OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1779152633
OL,3,CThree dead after San Diego mosque
OL,4,Cshooting as two teenage suspects found
OL,5,Cdead
OL,7,FAerial TV footage showed more than a
OL,8,Fdozen children holding hands and being
OL,9,Fwalked out of the car park of the
OL,10,Fcentre that is surrounded by scores of
OL,11,Fpolice vehicles.
OL,13,FPolice said they were called around
OL,14,F11.40am local time and declared an
OL,15,Factive shooter just after 12pm.
OL,17,FThey posted on social media at 1.06pm
OL,18,Fthat the threat had been "neutralised."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
