OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe mosque is in a neighbourhood of
OL,13,Fhomes, apartments and strip malls with
OL,14,FMiddle Eastern restaurants and markets.
OL,16,FGovernor Gavin Newsom said on X: "We
OL,17,Fare grateful to the first responders
OL,18,Fon the scene working to protect the
OL,19,Fcommunity and urge everyone to follow
OL,20,Fguidance from local authorities."
