OL,7,FThe Islamic Centre's website says its
OL,8,Fmission is to not only serve the
OL,9,FMuslim population but also "work with
OL,10,Fthe larger community to serve the less
OL,11,Ffortunate, to educate, and to better
OL,12,Four nation".
OL,14,FFive daily prayers are held there, and
OL,15,Fthe mosque works with other
OL,16,Forganisations and people of all faiths
OL,17,Fon social causes.
